    {
      "title": "Goals are too abstract to get support.",
      "created": 1748487522,
      "updated": 1748488040,
      "id": "6837cd5fea2d4727f8d5e12c",
      "views": 22,
      "lines": [
        {
          "text": "Goals are too abstract to get support.",
          "created": 1748487522,
          "updated": 1748488015,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a1a16072712b1aa935018c31d90b0ba9]",
          "created": 1748487523,
          "updated": 1748487525,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　1: Someone who wants to achieve a certain goal X and needs advice on how to achieve it.",
          "created": 1748487525,
          "updated": 1748487752,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　2: What exactly needs to be done to make it happen?",
          "created": 1748487753,
          "updated": 1748487798,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　　What lies beneath the surface that is difficult to see",
          "created": 1748487800,
          "updated": 1748487807,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　　What is the next action on the ground?",
          "created": 1748487808,
          "updated": 1748487820,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　　How can I give advice to someone who doesn't have the mood to think about it?",
          "created": 1748487820,
          "updated": 1748487874,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　　I don't know what you don't understand, you don't seem to understand everything.",
          "created": 1748488028,
          "updated": 1748488040,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　3: People who are taking specific actions to achieve goal X ask better questions.",
          "created": 1748487879,
          "updated": 1748487911,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　　I can talk about my experience of doing it first.",
          "created": 1748487911,
          "updated": 1748487942,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　　　I did A, I got it done, I did B, I got this too, I did C, I made this mistake.",
          "created": 1748487942,
          "updated": 1748487942,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　　Then we ask, \"What should we do about C?\" or \"Is there anything else we're overlooking?\" and other specific questions such as",
          "created": 1748487944,
          "updated": 1748487978,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　　Good questions elicit good answers.",
          "created": 1748487984,
          "updated": 1748487991,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "",
          "created": 1748487991,
          "updated": 1748487991,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "relevance",
          "created": 1748487531,
          "updated": 1748487547,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　 [People who want to do it but haven't.] ",
          "created": 1748487547,
          "updated": 1748487570,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "　 [Type-specific advice for contest applicants] ",
          "created": 1748487570,
          "updated": 1748487646,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
        {
          "text": "",
          "created": 1748487525,
          "updated": 1748487525,
          "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
        },
